{"tid":2495392,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"綜觀成個連登 係得阿妓post撐歐超聯","createTime":"2021-04-19T07:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T15:10:00.000Z","uid":5655,"like":24,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"dad48540b76923e8fb075aada7195cdcd043f2eb","tid":2495392,"uid":5655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:09:17.000Z","msg":"我都唔明有咩原因會撐<br />\n<br />\n。 每星期場場都有大戰<br />\n一開頭可能會好好睇<br />\n但當過咗一排之後<br />\n就會變到好悶<br />\n<br />\n。細會冇咗生存空間<br />\n其他球會冇得打歐超聯<br />\n姐係變相過去嘅李斯特城，阿積士等既黑馬唔會再出現<br />\n其他細會就會自然冇心機玩<br />\n變到好似NBA咁<br />\n得返一個聯賽出名<br />\n<br />\n。每年爭前四，護級都非常好睇<br />\n但歐超聯唔會降班<br />\n之後會出現好多風流波<br />\n<br />\n但我唔明點解阿妓會撐<br />\n我明 球會角度多咗錢 支持係正常<br />\n但係球迷角度 可觀性會大減好多<br />\n長久落去都足球喺負面發展<br />\n希望阿妓球迷理性"},{"pid":"913adcdea1f5c0b750e2008d01432e370505ad8a","tid":2495392,"uid":1262,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:11:01.000Z","msg":"你條波台過街老鼠"},{"pid":"eeb45d645cc5f957b5574c3a96352cc28f212101","tid":2495392,"uid":47268,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:11:57.000Z","msg":"班阿迷短視囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb9071db8634a21e59ee9a7fee3a4a8a83de93d2","tid":2495392,"uid":366932,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:13:39.000Z","msg":"因為阿妓喺未來都睇唔到有得踢歐聯既機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a8c31d6447028abecce9f55e8a83c1d9a23fdd","tid":2495392,"uid":5655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUnad463FgdvUS17p3gnGw2VVPRzmPqQTZVBcgmt318ha?filename=Zmw8WFT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZmw8WFT.png&h=7197cf42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6b14616ffa76b6aa3772eec44c498e8cf501c77","tid":2495392,"uid":47268,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:14:28.000Z","msg":"根本班中小型球會其實就係成個足球世界既地基<br /